<qti-assessment-item xmlns="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0" xmlns:m="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" identifier="Q36_v6" title="Q36_v6" time-dependent="false" adaptive="false" xsi:schemaLocation="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0 https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/schema/xsd/imsqti_asiv3p0_v1p0.xsd">
  <qti-response-declaration identifier="RESPONSE" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier">
    <qti-correct-response>
      <qti-value>ChoiceB</qti-value>
    </qti-correct-response>
  </qti-response-declaration>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="FEEDBACK" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SOLUTION" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SCORE" cardinality="single" base-type="float"><qti-default-value><qti-value>0</qti-value></qti-default-value></qti-outcome-declaration>
  <qti-item-body>
    <p>En una función de cine se vendieron entradas de adulto (a) y de niño (n). Se sabe que el número de entradas de cada tipo cumple el siguiente sistema de ecuaciones:</p>
    <div>
      <m:math>
        <m:mtable>
          <m:mtr>
            <m:mtd>
              <m:mrow>
                <m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mi>a</m:mi><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mi>n</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>8</m:mn>
              </m:mrow>
            </m:mtd>
          </m:mtr>
          <m:mtr>
            <m:mtd>
              <m:mrow>
                <m:mn>4</m:mn><m:mi>a</m:mi><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mi>n</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>22</m:mn>
              </m:mrow>
            </m:mtd>
          </m:mtr>
        </m:mtable>
      </m:math>
    </div>
    <p>¿Cuántas entradas de adulto y cuántas de niño se vendieron en esa función? Elige la alternativa que indica correctamente el par (a, n).</p>
    <qti-choice-interaction response-identifier="RESPONSE" shuffle="false" max-choices="1">
      
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceA">(a, n) = (2, 4)<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceA" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. Al reemplazar a = 2 y n = 4, la primera ecuación sí se cumple: 2·2 + 4 = 8. Pero la segunda no se cumple: 4·2 + 3·4 = 8 + 12 = 20, y 20 es distinto de 22.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceB">(a, n) = (1, 6)<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceB" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">¡Correcto! Al reemplazar a = 1 y n = 6, se cumple 2·1 + 6 = 2 + 6 = 8 y también 4·1 + 3·6 = 4 + 18 = 22. Por lo tanto, el par (1, 6) satisface las dos ecuaciones del sistema.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
      
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceC">(a, n) = (−1, 10)<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceC" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. Al reemplazar a = −1 y n = 10, la primera ecuación sí se cumple: 2·(−1) + 10 = −2 + 10 = 8. Pero la segunda no se cumple: 4·(−1) + 3·10 = −4 + 30 = 26, y 26 es distinto de 22.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
      
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceD">(a, n) = (4, 2)<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceD" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. Al reemplazar a = 4 y n = 2, la primera ecuación no se cumple: 2·4 + 2 = 8 + 2 = 10, y 10 es distinto de 8. Además, la segunda da 4·4 + 3·2 = 16 + 6 = 22, pero una solución del sistema debe cumplir ambas ecuaciones a la vez.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
    </qti-choice-interaction>
    <qti-feedback-block identifier="show" outcome-identifier="SOLUTION" show-hide="show">
      <qti-content-body>
        <p><strong>Resolución paso a paso del sistema</strong></p>
        <ol>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 1: Escribir el sistema</strong></p>
            <p>El problema entrega el siguiente sistema:</p>
            <m:math>
              <m:mtable>
                <m:mtr>
                  <m:mtd>
                    <m:mrow>
                      <m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mi>a</m:mi><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mi>n</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>8</m:mn>
                    </m:mrow>
                  </m:mtd>
                </m:mtr>
                <m:mtr>
                  <m:mtd>
                    <m:mrow>
                      <m:mn>4</m:mn><m:mi>a</m:mi><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mi>n</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>22</m:mn>
                    </m:mrow>
                  </m:mtd>
                </m:mtr>
              </m:mtable>
            </m:math>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 2: Despejar una variable de la primera ecuación</strong></p>
            <p>De</p>
            <m:math>
              <m:mrow>
                <m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mi>a</m:mi><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mi>n</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>8</m:mn>
              </m:mrow>
            </m:math>
            <p>despejamos <strong>n</strong>:</p>
            <m:math>
              <m:mrow>
                <m:mi>n</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>8</m:mn><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mi>a</m:mi>
              </m:mrow>
            </m:math>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 3: Sustituir en la segunda ecuación</strong></p>
            <p>Reemplazamos</p>
            <m:math>
              <m:mrow>
                <m:mi>n</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>8</m:mn><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mi>a</m:mi>
              </m:mrow>
            </m:math>
            <p>en</p>
            <m:math>
              <m:mrow>
                <m:mn>4</m:mn><m:mi>a</m:mi><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mi>n</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>22</m:mn>
              </m:mrow>
            </m:math>
            <p>y queda:</p>
            <m:math>
              <m:mrow>
                <m:mn>4</m:mn><m:mi>a</m:mi><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mrow><m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mn>8</m:mn><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mi>a</m:mi><m:mo>)</m:mo></m:mrow><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>22</m:mn>
              </m:mrow>
            </m:math>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 4: Resolver la ecuación resultante</strong></p>
            <p>Distribuimos el 3:</p>
            <m:math>
              <m:mrow>
                <m:mn>4</m:mn><m:mi>a</m:mi><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>24</m:mn><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>6</m:mn><m:mi>a</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>22</m:mn>
              </m:mrow>
            </m:math>
            <p>Reducimos términos semejantes:</p>
            <m:math>
              <m:mrow>
                <m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mi>a</m:mi><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>24</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>22</m:mn>
              </m:mrow>
            </m:math>
            <p>Restamos 24 en ambos lados:</p>
            <m:math>
              <m:mrow>
                <m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mi>a</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>2</m:mn>
              </m:mrow>
            </m:math>
            <p>Dividimos por −2:</p>
            <m:math>
              <m:mrow>
                <m:mi>a</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>1</m:mn>
              </m:mrow>
            </m:math>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 5: Encontrar el valor de n</strong></p>
            <p>Sustituimos</p>
            <m:math>
              <m:mrow>
                <m:mi>a</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>1</m:mn>
              </m:mrow>
            </m:math>
            <p>en</p>
            <m:math>
              <m:mrow>
                <m:mi>n</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>8</m:mn><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mi>a</m:mi>
              </m:mrow>
            </m:math>
            <p>y obtenemos:</p>
            <m:math>
              <m:mrow>
                <m:mi>n</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>8</m:mn><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>8</m:mn><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>6</m:mn>
              </m:mrow>
            </m:math>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 6: Verificar la solución</strong></p>
            <p>Primera ecuación:</p>
            <m:math>
              <m:mrow>
                <m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>6</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>6</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>8</m:mn>
              </m:mrow>
            </m:math>
            <p>Segunda ecuación:</p>
            <m:math>
              <m:mrow>
                <m:mn>4</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mo>·</m:mo><m:mn>6</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>4</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>18</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>22</m:mn>
              </m:mrow>
            </m:math>
            <p>Se cumplen las dos ecuaciones.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Conclusión</strong></p>
            <p>La solución del sistema es</p>
            <m:math>
              <m:mrow>
                <m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mi>a</m:mi><m:mo>,</m:mo><m:mi>n</m:mi><m:mo>)</m:mo><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mo>,</m:mo><m:mn>6</m:mn><m:mo>)</m:mo>
              </m:mrow>
            </m:math>
            <p>Por lo tanto, la alternativa correcta es <strong>ChoiceB</strong>.</p>
          </li>
        </ol>
      </qti-content-body>
    </qti-feedback-block>
  </qti-item-body>
  <qti-response-processing>
    <qti-response-condition>
      <qti-response-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SCORE">
          <qti-base-value base-type="float">1</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceC</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceC</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceD</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceD</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else>
    </qti-response-condition>
  </qti-response-processing>
</qti-assessment-item>